        "Node name for S&R": "CLIPTextEncode"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "A vast lake surface like a mirror, soft morning light spreads across the water casting gentle golden ripples, the giant rocks by the lake are gently covered with moss, showing the passage of time and age. A young woman dressed in traditional Hanfu stands on the stone, her hair styled in an elegant high bun, adorned with delicate cloud-patterned hairpins, her face crystal-clear and mirror-like, with a faint calmness and concentration between her eyebrows and eyes. Her two hands lightly grip the piano keys, her fingers dance fluidly on the keys, the curves of her fingertips intertwine with light and shadow as if she is conveying each delicate note to the lake. Distant mountains rise in layers, shrouded in mist, the lush trees at the foot of the mountains, with occasional soft bird songs among the branches, adding a touch of liveliness to the scene. The overall composition, rendered with the delicate realism of photography, shows distinct layers of light and shadow, the fine lines on her face and the movements of her hands are vividly lifelike, as if one can hear the soft echo of the piano keys being gently brushed and feel the subtle ripples of lake water gently lapping against the rocks."
      ]
    },
